1. Overview

Project Name: Applogy Official Website
Purpose:
Create a modern, fast, and SEO-optimized website for Applogy, an AI app studio that develops creative, user-friendly, and App Store–ready AI applications.
The website should reflect innovation, creativity, and trust — highlighting Applogy’s portfolio and linking users directly to the App Store.

Tech Stack:

Frontend: Next.js 14 (React 18, App Router)

Styling: Tailwind CSS

Deployment: Vercel

Analytics: Google Analytics 4

SEO: Optimized metadata, OG tags, sitemap, and structured data

2. Goals

Strengthen Applogy’s brand presence online.

Drive traffic and conversions to App Store product pages.

Showcase all published apps dynamically, fetched from App Store API.

Ensure fast loading times, excellent mobile UX, and modern AI-inspired UI.

3. Target Audience

English-speaking users (mainly U.S. App Store users).

Tech-savvy and creative individuals.

People looking for AI-based tools or entertainment apps.

Media & tech reviewers.

